deleted": 0, "content": "", "content_rendered": "", "last_modified": 1695380778, "replies": 50, "id": 976305}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1630643913", "name": "apple", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1630643913", "title": "Apple", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple", "topics": 23603, "footer": "", "header": "设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。", "title_alternative": "Apple", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913", "stars": 2711, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 184, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"id": 427688, "username": "heyenyan", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/heyenyan", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5448/5873/427688_mini.png?m=1692921443", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5448/5873/427688_normal.png?m=1692921443", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5448/5873/427688_large.png?m=1692921443", "created": 1562550808, "last_modified": 1692921443}, "last_reply_by": "cnmilkmilk", "last_touched": 1695408851, "title": "iPhone 15 pro Type-C 问题记录", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/976233", "created": 1695368273, "deleted": 0, "content": "自带数据线 C-C ，Anker 充电头正常充电。插入笔记本 C 口正常充电、传数据、网络共享。\r\n\r\n华为快冲 A-C 线(紫色口)，不能充电&不能传数据。\r\n\r\n小米平板自带数据线 A-C ，只能充电&不能传数据。\r\n\r\n小米手机自带 A-C 线，不能充电&不能传数据。\r\n\r\n笔记本自带 C-C 线，可以充电&传数据&网络共享。\r\n\r\n剃须刀 A-C 线，不能充电。\r\n\r\n车上一条不知名 A-C 线，无法充电！！\r\n\r\n我真的服了啊，车上只有两个 A 口，只能把平板的线拿来放车上了！！！", "content_rendered": "<p>自带数据线 C-C ，Anker 充电头正常充电。插入笔记本 C 口正常充电、传数据、网络共享。</p>\n<p>华为快冲 A-C 线(紫色口)，不能充电&amp;不能传数据。</p>\n<p>小米平板自带数据线 A-C ，只能充电&amp;不能传数据。</p>\n<p>小米手机自带 A-C 线，不能充电&amp;不能传数据。</p>\n<p>笔记本自带 C-C 线，可以充电&amp;传数据&amp;网络共享。</p>\n<p>剃须刀 A-C 线，不能充电。</p>\n<p>车上一条不知名 A-C 线，无法充电！！</p>\n<p>我真的服了啊，车上只有两个 A 口，只能把平板的线拿来放车上了！！！</p>\n", "last_modified": 1695368273, "replies": 45, "id": 976233}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_large.png?m=1660301119", "name": "create", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_normal.png?m=1660301119", "title": "分享创造", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/create", "topics": 21345, "footer": "", "header": "欢迎你在这里发布自己的最新作品！", "title_alternative": "Create", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_mini.png?m=1660301119", "stars": 5034, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 17, "parent_node_name": "geek"}, "member": {"id": 321076, "username": "Dreamerwwr", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Dreamerwwr", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d56f/8723/321076_mini.png?m=1534401124", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d56f/8723/321076_normal.png?m=1534401124", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d56f/8723/321076_large.png?m=1534401124", "created": 1528345210, "last_modified": 1534401124}, "last_reply_by": "someonedeng", "last_touched": 1695393561, "title": "有没有减轻人力提重物的发明？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/976214", "created": 1695366455, "deleted": 0, "content": "爸妈年纪大了，常年提重物、搬重物身体出问题了，让歇着还不听，有没有什么发明可以减轻提重物、搬重物的负担？\r\n\r\n提重物：经常提着一个大水桶，里面都是饲料，需要在多个猪栏围间穿梭来喂食\r\n搬重物：经常需要把一大袋玉米搬来进行粉碎\r\n\r\n有没有什么发明能减轻这种活动引起的消耗呢？", "content_rendered": "<p>爸妈年纪大了，常年提重物、搬重物身体出问题了，让歇着还不听，有没有什么发明可以减轻提重物、搬重物的负担？</p>\n<p>提重物：经常提着一个大水桶，里面都是饲料，需要在多个猪栏围间穿梭来喂食\n搬重物：经常需要把一大袋玉米搬来进行粉碎</p>\n<p>有没有什么发明能减轻这种活动引起的消耗呢？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1695366455, "replies": 38, "id": 976214}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1630643913", "name": "apple", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1630643913", "title